race.comment: TROPIC SANDS (4) couldn't have been more impressive saluting at the Gold Coast last time out and will have taken a bunch of confidence from that dominant victory. Winning rider Peisley sticks in the stirrups and should give backers a great sight up on speed. GREY NORTHERN (6) has put back-to-back wins together and it's hard to knock mares in form. Could easily bring up the hat-trick here against this field decimated by scratchings. UNCOMMON VALOUR (1) loves racing at this track only missing a drum once in eight spins. Can bounce back after a plain performance last time out. OUTBURST (5) best of the rest from the inside alley.
